Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那你是密史特拉來的啊  真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們那東西好吃  美女也多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停戰以來快有半年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能活著看到這天真是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  J
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  怎能這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰利品  分你點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能  能收到如此貴重之物  感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  軍曹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦  據說只要能和司號兵拉近關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就總能順利的聽到撤退的號角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經不徵兵了  竟然還能看到新兵  真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志願的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了學習音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說出來很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵  你名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫空深彼方
